    "Multiple datasets can leverage the same BigTable instance, amortizing its cost across them.",
    "The numbers in Fig. 2e provide the cost for such a scenario.",
    "(2) The number of annotations and the number (and type) of columns determine the storage requirements for the annotation databases.",
    "Scaling with the size of the dataset volume varies between datasets especially because synapse densities are different by almost an order of magnitude between mammalian and insect brains.",
